trans-unit.source: Represents a runtime handle for a module.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en runtime-referens för en modul.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>, <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A>, and <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A> methods provide efficient resolution of metadata tokens to runtime handles for fields, methods, and types in the current module.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>, <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A>, och <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A>metoder ger effektiv lösning av metadata token runtime referenser för fält, metoder och typer i den aktuella modulen.</xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A> </xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A> </xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>
